Odaily Planet Daily News According to the official announcement, Binance will update the fiat currency trading market maker program at 08:00 (Eastern Time Zone 8) on March 24, 2025. Main updates:
From 08:00 (Eastern Time Zone 8) on March 24, 2025, the new EUR market level will be added to the fiat currency market maker program. The review level of this market will be adjusted from one level to two levels;
The percentage requirement of the transaction volume of the maker (Maker) of level 1 is 0.5%; the percentage requirement of the transaction volume of the maker (Maker) of level 2 is 1.0%;
After passing, the maker (Maker) fee rate of level 1 is -0.005%; the maker (Maker) fee rate of level 2 is -0.010%;
The new fiat currency market qualification review will take effect at 08:00 (Eastern Time Zone 8) on March 24, 2025. Market maker accounts will be reviewed weekly based on the new activity review mechanism;
From 08:00 (ET on April 1, 2025), maker fee rebates will be issued based on the market maker's trading performance in the designated spot fiat market last week.
